credit_line: Gift of Stephen W. Brener and Carol B. Brener
title: Domino
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description: Rectangular, in the form of a beige domino game piece with ten black dots, four above black, incised, horizontal line in center, six below, with brass bolt situated at center of incised line. Sides and reverse are black, reverse inscribed "Bull & Bell Ropemaker, With E. Cuthbert's Compts." Lid hinged on left side, end protrudes slightly on right for thumb catch. Striker on left vertical side.
name: Matchsafe
